---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Me - Joseph Oforkansi">

  <section class="about-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Me</h1>
      <p class="tagline">Embedded Systems Engineer | Firmware | Hardware | Integration</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about-content">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>Who I Am</h2>
      <p>
        I'm Joseph Oforkansi, an embedded systems engineer passionate about building reliable, real-time systems from prototype to production.
      </p>
      <p>
        My focus is on firmware development, hardware-software integration, microcontroller programming, and optimizing embedded designs for performance, power, and reliability.
      </p>
      <p>
        I enjoy working at the low level — debugging with JTAG/SWD, interfacing sensors, implementing communication protocols (I2C, SPI, UART, CAN), and bringing ideas to life in hardware.
      </p>

      <h2>What I Do</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Develop firmware for microcontrollers (ARM Cortex-M/A) and embedded Linux systems</li>
        <li>Design and prototype PCBs (using KiCad)</li>
        <li>Integrate sensors, actuators, and wireless modules</li>
        <li>Use RTOS (FreeRTOS, Zephyr) for real-time applications</li>
        <li>Debug and optimize embedded systems for production</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Why I Love This Work</h2>
      <p>
        There's something special about seeing code run on real hardware — making things move, sense the world, communicate, and solve problems in the physical world.
        I love the challenge of constrained resources, tight timing, and the satisfaction of a stable, efficient system.
      </p>

      <!-- Add photo or personal touch later -->
      <!-- <img src="/images/profile.jpg" alt="Joseph Oforkansi" class="profile-photo" /> -->

      <a href="#contact" class="btn">Let's talk about your project</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .about-hero {
    min-height: 50vh;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #0f0f1a, #0a0a15);
    padding: 6rem 1rem 4rem;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    color: #00d4ff;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .about-content {
    padding: 5rem 1rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    margin: 0;
    color: white;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin: 2.5rem 0 1rem;
    color: #00d4ff;
  }

  p, ul {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: #c0c0ff;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  ul li {
    margin: 1rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.8rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  ul li::before {
    content: "→";
    color: #00d4ff;
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    background: #00d4ff;
    color: black;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    background: #0099cc;
  }

  /* Optional profile photo style */
  .profile-photo {
    width: 220px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    display: block;
    border: 4px solid #00d4ff33;
  }
</style>